{
  "stem": "7157.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You wouldn't talk to anyone.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You wouldn't-- certainly about things like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My educated guess would be no, because, at this point, the Jews were already-- most of them were gone.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And, you know, this was 1944, I'm saying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I remember-- oh my God, it was so high.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I looked down, and it was like-- you know, at least to a little kid, it was like-- it looked like yards and yards away that I had to jump.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I jumped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we jumped.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In fact, I had-- in Europe, you wore long socks in those days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I had like a rubber band around my socks to hold them up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when I jumped, this rubber band really dug into my foot.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I remember how terrible that hurt.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It just hurt something awful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But we jumped and started running towards-- towards a farmhouse.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and it's really strange.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Most of the people didn't follow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We knew-- here's a case for being Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We survived because we knew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The other people didn't have the kind of fear we had, you know, so it was-- Some of them, later-- we heard shots, or I heard shots.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "So some of them must have started jumping and running from the train.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "But unfortunately, at this point, it was too late.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Night-- it was-- it was nighttime-- definitely dark.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But, you know, the flashlights and the lights were on these people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of them, at least from what we heard, did not survive.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took us in, and they hid us in these farmhouses until kind of that search.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because the Germans started searching.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans were very exact.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They started searching homes and searching farmhouses.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But basically, they hid us in these-- in this home-- in these farmhouses.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
